<SUMMARY>
SUMMARY:

 On August 5, 1993, the Department of Commerce published the preliminary results of its administrative review of the
antidumping duty order on silicon metal from Brazil. The review period is March 29, 1991 through June 30, 1992. The
review covers four manufacturers/exporters. 



We gave interested parties an opportunity to comment on the preliminary results. Based on our analysis of the comments
