is soliciting public comment. Copies of the preliminary report may be obtained by calling the U.S. Patent and Trademark
Office at (703) 305-9300 or by sending a written request to the Commissioner of Patents and Trademarks, U.S.
Patent and Trademark Office, Box 4, Washington, DC 20231, marked to the attention to Terri A. Southwick, Office of
