the ``contributed importantly'' test of Group Eligibility Requirements of the Trade Act was met. The Department's
survey shows that customers accounting for a major portion of the subject firm's sales decline in FY 1994 increased
their imported purchases of plywood while decreasing their purchases from the subject firm.



