94-4 Lost Reference Sources at Brooks Air Force Base in San Antonio, Texas



One of the AO reporting guidelines notes that any serious deficiency in management or procedural controls in a major
area can be considered an abnormal occurrence.



Date and Place_

1993; Armstrong Laboratory, Brooks Air Force Base (AFB); San Antonio, Texas.



