Principles/Process 


 Must be a joint action by FHWA and FTA.
 Must be based on a serious examination of the planning process that documents the adequacy of the planning process.
However, the workload involved in reviewing the planning process for approximately 135 MPOs once every 3 years combined
with other oversight and administrative responsibilities demands a process that utilizes and builds on the other
oversight functions including TIP findings, Unified Planning Work Program approvals and conformity findings.

